      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.047301697731022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんってば\n私もちょっとは反省してるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I’m sorry.\nI do regret what I did‚ really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.847301697731018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんと話が出来るって分かって\nここのところテンション上がりっぱなしで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m just so excited that I get to talk to Mei\nthat I’ve been so hyper about it lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.664321719972708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.90299351215359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないな……でも、麻奈からも言ってくれよ\nさすがにこう毎日だと俺の身がもたない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it. Just please tell her to cool it a little.\nDoing this every night is really taking a toll on my body.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9696601788203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
