    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（……一体どうしたというんだ。グループ分けを）\n（提案した時を上回る冷気を感じるんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What is their deal? They haven’t acted this cold towards me)\n(since the day I proposed the group split.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.31622936673789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "…………あの……沙季？\n一体みんなどうしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Saki?\nWhat’s wrong with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.95239949022371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "何かご用でしょうか？　ゲス……\nいえ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What business brings you here‚ scum?\nIt’s nothing‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4190661568904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？\n…………今、なんて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nWhat did you just call me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.96670087891535,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 799.999999999983,
          "startTime": 73.40003421224868
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（――でも、まだ琴乃が残っている）\n（事務所に入った当初こそ、俺に対して冷たかったが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Kotono is still here.)\n(She’s been cold to me ever since she joined the agency‚)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.36670087891535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（これまで時間をかけて強い信頼関係を築いてきた）\n（その関係は、簡単に揺るがない自信があるからな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(but since then‚ we’ve built up a strong foundation of trust between us.)\n(And I have confidence that our trust can’t be shaken so easily.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.90923129068103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.74256462401436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "辞めて下さい\n今すぐ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please quit.\nRight now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.73827893879304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "間違いなく、みんなに嫌われちゃってるね\n{user}くん、これって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No mistaking it; everyone hates you.\n{user}‚ could this be…",
        "id": ""
