      "startTime": 108.16654792772019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さんと芽衣は\n付き合ってるのかって聞かれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ and they asked if you and I\nwere dating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.56654792772012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "いやー{user}さんの部屋で\n毎晩ゲームしてただけ、って言ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And wellll‚ I told them all I was doing\nwas playing games with you in your room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.15546845740356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 118.3300262794948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
