      "text": "『それを付き合ってるって言うのよ』\nって言われて、じゃあそうなのかなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they said‚ “That means you’re dating.”\nAnd it made me go‚ huh‚ maybe they’re right.",
        "id": ""
